 "Title":"Relates to the use of assumed and corporate names pertaining to household goods moving",
 "Summary":"Relates to the use of assumed and corporate names by companies in the business of household goods moving; provides that companies may not use the words \"mover\", \"moving\", or \"relocation service\" or any abbreviation or derivative thereof unless approved by the commissioner of transportation.",
 "LawSection":"Business Corporation Law",
